hen Studiums der Gefühle.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aEmotionen. 4aGefühle. 4aSinnlichkeit. 4aaffektive Haltungen. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh1 aAdloff, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAlbrecht, Yvonne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBernhardt, Fabian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDehne, Max, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDiefenbach, Aletta , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDiefenbach, Aletta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHerbrik, Regine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKnoblauch, Hubert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeckel, Sighard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPritz, Sarah Miriam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRacleș, Andreea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRöttger-Rössler, Birgitt, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSauer, Birgit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSauerborn, Elgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aScheve, Christian von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchützeichel, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSenge, Konstanze, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStodulka, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSökefeld, Nina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aUral, Nu